oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Thesaurus Transcriptions: Part 13
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: This recording features songs on Hank Snow's album "The Thesaurus Transcriptions." This is part thirteen of fifteen tapes for this album. This tape is twenty-seven of an unidentified number of tapes.
